{
  "stem": "22447.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after 21 days, I was in a place called Tidworth, Tidworth Hospital, military hospital, I got posted back to the depot in Hounslow so I went back to Hounslow.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from there, I went to-- from there, you get posted to a draft, whatever draft was going where they needed new troops.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You said, it was luck of the draw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I got posted back to the West Kents for some reason, because there was a draft on that to the Middle East.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from there-- you have to pass a medical and the doctor there said, oh, you've been in the hospital 22 days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're not fit for this type of thing, and I got sent back to Lingfield, another race course, Lingfield.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At Lingfield, when we got there, there was an MCC flag flying and the old-fashioned [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lucas ?] head lights, all the way round the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, I said to the drive, I said, what are these lights for?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, oh, when there's an air raid, we flood light the camp so the Germans know that the prison's over here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's the safest place in England.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the-- the flag was an MCC flag was because the colonel in charge of the-- Lieutenant Colonel French, his father was a field marshal in the First World War so he had a bit of sway.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, if you play cricket, you'll be all right here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- he was a member of the MCC so he had this flag flying.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after that, I got posted back to Chatham.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
